Run a code in a docker image

Source: R/run.R
docker_run_code.Rd

Run a code as a string in a docker image

docker_run_code(code, docker_image, volumes = NULL)

Arguments

code

An expression or string of R code
docker_image

A docker image name
volumes

Volume mapping from host to container

Examples

library("altRnative")

# With string
docker_run_code("a = 1 + 1", "ismailsunni/gnur-3.6.1-debian-geospatial")
#> Detected API version '1.40' is above max version '1.39'; downgrading
#> [1] "Full command"
#> [1] "Rscript"   "-e"        "a = 1 + 1"
#> <docker_run_output>
#>   $container:
#>     <docker_container>
#>       id: 70c040acfbc0f16ca037e121af4f4f88c3eb1f869cf12ede4f94d37357bcd5a4
#>       name: confident_goldberg
#> 
#>   $logs:
#>     

# With expression
